
<p style="margin-left:0" align="justify">MODENA's success as a trusted brand is exemplified by the various awards and certifications that it has been awarded by reputable and independent organizations.</p>
<p style="margin-left:0">
<ul class="list-no-style">
 <p style="margin-left:0px";><li>MODENA won multilple awards from international research company GfK in 2010, 2011 and 2012 as the number one consumer choice in the product categories of Built-in Hob, Built-in Oven, Freestanding Cooker and Exhaust Hood, with over half the market share in Indonesia.</li></p>

 <p style="margin-left:0px";><li>ISO 9001 - 2015 Quality Management System certification by TUV Rheinland and consistent implementation of Lean Six Sigma in order to attain superior operational system and procedures.</li></p>

 <p style="margin-left:0px";><li>Based  on the research conducted by MARS (the exclusive licensed holder of American  Customer Satisfaction Index in Indonesia) MODENA has been successfully selected  as the only cooker brand that was awarded 5 Stars Quality Global Customer  Satisfaction Standard (GCSS) for the cooker/stove category in Indonesia. The  achievement includes the highest customer satisfaction index (CSI) on customer  expectation, customer loyalty, perceived quality and perceived value.</li></p>
 <p style="margin-left:0px";><li>MODENA successfully won the Indonesia Best Brand Award 2013 for built-in hob category.</li></p>
</ul>
